---
title: All-American Pork & Caramelised Onion Pie with Cheesy Potato Topping & Cucumber Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs a smokey, veggie-loaded pork base full of flavour, then tops the pie off with decadent and delicious gooey Cheddar potato mash. Finishing the meal off under the grill ensures you're eating your tasty creation as fast as possible!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65e92acf904479aa17a25246-7ac98a4b.jpeg
